000Z","msg":"人地打Boxing，富德泰拳，九唔搭八，唔理你好正常"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:12:14.000Z","msg":"講明話用boxing同佢揪有幾九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"第一：<br />\n泰拳同拳擊係截然不同既運動黎，比賽黎對曹星如的確無意思。<br />\n講緊你就算肯打Boxing例，就只會好似之前Conor打Mayweather咁，根本唔係對手 。<br />\n拉得成呢場特例賽事，都係為<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">錢</span></span>咋<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦你試下揾Cody同Romanchenko打，人地彩你有味啦<br />\n<br />\n第二：<br />\n曹星如唔係頂尖拳手，但作為一個拳擊手都要精進拳擊技術，升Rank架都要<br />\n<br />\n同富德打，冒住受傷風險，無Rank升<br />\n<br />\n講精進技術尋求挑戰，有咩好得過打Pro Boxer？定叫呀Jose Aldo打下散猜練MMA?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本放諸世界，Pro Boxer唔會Accept個MMA or Muay Thai Fightet打Boxer例係正常到無人有既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647854b3e46ba109885caf17d00ca54dfbbb0dfa","tid":678570,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e7f82fcd2a4e351da261b329a943bee312b19bf","tid":678570,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aae7fba68ef8939ebb53041a4d0e92a3c23596f","tid":678570,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95acc2611e7dfe2b8a2d11daa60d20e787baddb2","tid":678570,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"佢會話，日日都想同佢打<br />\n不過未好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"打多次河野公平先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"河野公平咩，上次咁都贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"打贏果個要入廠<br />\n打輸果個咩事都無"},{"pid":"c32cc538f543b185d9f3b9b63a81e82a62c98643","tid":678570,"uid":99816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b36356e7830bcc959947f7235799530102dd0918","tid":678570,"uid":24034,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20745de140